Package: fgczquartotemplate
Title: FGCZ Quarto Report Templates and Shared Styling
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Witold", "Wolski", , "witold@ethz.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shared Quarto report assets for FGCZ analysis packages
    (ezRun, prolfqua): a common format YAML, SCSS theme, HTML header, and
    starter report templates, plus helpers to stage them next to a .qmd
    and render.
